The paper discusses neural networks and their implementation of models, which falls under the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the concept of algorithmic complexity, which is relevant to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of datasets and classification also suggests relevance to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the discussion of recurrent and deep networks suggests relevance to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
